cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image quality assessment. The use of deep learning methods also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The Siamese framework used in the proposed method is also a common technique in deep learning for similarity learning, which could place this paper in the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Finally, the use of predictive coding theory in the proposed method suggests that it could also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
